------------------OBJECT, TYPES AND METHODS-----------------------
create type PERSON_TYP as object
(
LNAME VARCHAR2 (12),
FNAME VARCHAR2 (12),
DOB DATE,
MEMBER FUNCTION AGE RETURN NUMBER,
PRAGMA RESTRICT_REFERENCES(AGE, WNDS)
)
NOT FINAL;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TYPE PHONE_TYP AS OBJECT(
    ph_type VARCHAR2(25),
    ph_num VARCHAR2(25)
);

CREATE TYPE phone_tab AS TABLE OF
PHONE_TYP;
/

create or replace type EMP_TYP under PERSON_TYP
(
SEX CHAR(1),
RATE NUMBER,
COMMISSION NUMBER, 
START_DATE DATE,
END_DATE DATE,
MEMBER FUNCTION emp_duration RETURN number,
PRAGMA RESTRICT_REFERENCES(emp_duration, WNDS));
/

create or replace type CUST_TYP under PERSON_TYP
(
CREDIT_LIMIT NUMBER
);
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TYPE address_typ AS OBJECT 
(
address_type	varchar2(10),
STREET VARCHAR2(30),
CITY VARCHAR2 (15),
STATE VARCHAR2 (2),
ZIP NUMBER (10));
/

CREATE TYPE address_tab AS TABLE OF
address_typ;
/


create or replace type body PERSON_TYP as
member function AGE return number 
is
   var_age number;
   begin
      var_age := trunc((sysdate - self.dob)/365.25);
      return var_age;
   end;
end;
/


create or replace type body EMP_TYP as
member function emp_duration return number
is
   v_years number;
   begin
      v_years := trunc((self.end_date - self.start_date)/365.25);
      return v_years;
   end;
end;
/

--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table O_EMPLOYEE
--------------------------------------------------------
CREATE TABLE O_EMPLOYEE(
	EMPLOYEE_ID NUMBER(38,0) not null,
	EMPLOYEE EMP_TYP,
	ADDRESS ADDRESS_TAB,
	PHONE PHONE_TAB,
	JOB_TITLE_ID NUMBER,
	CONSTRAINT EMPLOYEE_JOB_TITLE_FK FOREIGN KEY (JOB_TITLE_ID) REFERENCES JOB_TITLE (JOB_TITLE_ID),
	CONSTRAINT EMPLOYEE_NO_PK PRIMARY KEY (EMPLOYEE_ID))
	NESTED TABLE ADDRESS STORE AS nested_address_table
    NESTED TABLE PHONE STORE AS nested_phone_table;
--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table O_CUSTOMER
--------------------------------------------------------
CREATE TABLE O_CUSTOMER(
  CUSTOMER_ID NUMBER NOT NULL,
  CUSTOMER CUST_TYP,
  ADDRESS ADDRESS_TAB,
  PHONE PHONE_TAB,
  BALANCE NUMBER(10,0),
  BRANCH_ID NUMBER,
  REGION_ID NUMBER,
  CONSTRAINT CUSTOMER_ID_PK PRIMARY KEY (CUSTOMER_ID),
  CONSTRAINT CUSTOMER_BRANCH_ID_FK FOREIGN KEY (BRANCH_ID) REFERENCES BRANCH (BRANCH_ID),
  --CONSTRAINT CUSTOMER_REGION_FK FOREIGN KEY (REGION_ID) REFERENCES REGION (REGION_ID)
)NESTED TABLE ADDRESS STORE AS nested_address_table1
 NESTED TABLE PHONE STORE AS nested_phone_table1;
--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table O_WAREHOUSE
--------------------------------------------------------
CREATE TABLE O_WAREHOUSE(
    WAREHOUSE_ID NUMVER NOT NULL,
    STREET_ADDRESS VARCHAR2(30),
    CITY VARCHAR2(30),
    STATE VARCHAR2(5),
    ZIP NUMBER(10,0),
    PHONE PHONE_TAB,
    REGION_ID NUMBER,
    CONSTRAINT WAREHOUSE_ID_PK PRIMARY KEY (WAREHOUSE_ID),
    --CONSTRAINT WAREHOUSES_REGION_ID_FK FOREIGN KEY (REGION_ID) REFERENCES REGION (REGION_ID)
)NESTED TABLE PHONE STORE AS NESTED_PHONE_TABLE2;
--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table O_ORDERS
--------------------------------------------------------
CREATE TABLE O_ORDERS(
    ORDER_ID NUMBER(25,0) NOT NULL,
    ORDER_DATE DATE,
    REQUIRED_DATE DATE,
    SHIPPED_DATE DATE,
    SHIPPING_CHARGE NUMBER(10,0),
    SUBTOTAL NUMBER(10,0),
    TOTAL NUMBER(10,0),
    S_M_ID NUMBER(10,0),
    CUSTOMER_ID NUMBER,
    BRANCH_ID NUMBER,
    EMPLOYEE_ID NUMBER(10,0),
    CONSTRAINT ORDERS_ORDERID_PK PRIMARY KEY (ORDER_ID),
    --CONSTRAINT ORDERS_S_METHOD_FK FOREIGN KEY (S_M_ID) REFERENCES SHIPPING_METHOD (S_METHOD_ID),
    --CONSTRAINT ORDERS_CUSTOMER_FK FOREIGN KEY (CUSTOMER_ID) REFERENCES CUSTOMER (CUSTOMER_ID),
    --CONSTRAINT ORDERS_BRANCH_FK FOREIGN KEY (BRANCH_ID) REFERENCES BRANCH (BRANCH_ID),
    --CONSTRAINT ORDERS_EMPLOYEE_FK FOREIGN KEY (EMPLOYEE_ID) REFERENCES O_EMPLOYEE (EMPLOYEE_ID)
);
--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table O_ORDER_LINE
--------------------------------------------------------
CREATE TABLE O_ORDER_LINE(
    ORDER_LINE_ID NUMBER(10,0) NOT NULL,
    QTY NUMBER(10,0),
    ORDER_ID NUMBER(10,0),
    PRODUCT_ID NUMBER(10,0),
    CONSTRAINT ORDER_LINE_ID_PK PRIMARY KEY (ORDER_LINE_ID),
    CONSTRAINT OL_ORDER_FK FOREIGN KEY (ORDER_ID) REFERENCES ORDERS (ORDER_ID),
    CONSTRAINT OL_PRODUCT_FK FOREIGN KEY (PRODUCT_ID) REFERENCES PRODUCT (PRODUCT_ID)
);
--------------------------------------------------------
--  DDL for Table WAREHOUSE
--------------------------------------------------------
  CREATE TABLE "NIRAJ"."WAREHOUSE" 
   (	"WAREHOUSE_ID" NUMBER(15,0), 
	"STREET_ADDRESS" VARCHAR2(30 BYTE), 
	"CITY" VARCHAR2(30 BYTE), 
	"STATE" VARCHAR2(5 BYTE), 
	"POSTAL_CODE" NUMBER(10,0), 
	"PHONE" VARCHAR2(15 BYTE), 
	"REGION_ID" NUMBER(15,0)
   ) PCTFREE 10 PCTUSED 40 INITRANS 1 MAXTRANS 255 NOCOMPRESS LOGGING
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1 BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "USERS" ;
